CM_ SG_ 2216424431 HS_Ctl1CRC_Rx2 "The CRC is defined as follows:
 • Length: 8 bits
 • Polynomial: x^8+x^5+x^3+x^2+x+1
 • Initial Value: FFh
 • Input Data Reflection: Not reflected
 • Result Data Reflection: Not reflected
 • XOR value: FFh

SAE makes no claim of the functional saf";
