CM_ SG_ 2216424431 HS_HiUBusPasIslnTestCmd_Rx2 "Command for the High Voltage Energy Storage System (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack) to perform a passive electrical isolation test on the high voltage bus.

A passive isolation test uses additional circuitry (e.g. a high impedance network) to ";
CM_ SG_ 2216424431 HS_HiUBusAcvIslnTestCmd_Rx2 "Command for the High Voltage Energy Storage System (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack) to perform an active electrical isolation test on the high voltage bus.

An active isolation test might use a generated signal (e.g. an injected AC signal) and";
CM_ SG_ 2216424431 HS_PwrDwnCmd_Rx2 "Command to shut down the High Voltage Energy Storage System (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack).  A normal power-down may involve steps that take some period of time (tests, writing of data, etc.).  However, an emergency power-down should shut down";
CM_ SG_ 2216424431 HS_HiUBusCnctCmd_Rx2 "Command to connect the High Voltage Energy Storage System (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack) to the high-voltage bus.  The emergency contactor closure request may be used in situations where one or more faults in the hybrid powertrain prevent norm";
