CM_ SG_ 2364535585 CRC_PGN61427 "The end-to-end crc is calculated over the first seven bytes of the CAN frame. The end-to-end crc is calculated with the WCDMA-8 (x^8 +x^7 +x^4 +x^3 +x +1)
polynomial.";
CM_ SG_ 2364535585 Counter_PGN61427 "The message counter is incremented by one for each new message. If the message counter exceeds the message counter maximum value, it start again by 0.
