CM_ SG_ 2633785075 HS_TotAccumdCh "The total accumulated amp hours which have flowed through High Voltage Energy Storage System (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack).  This parameter is the sum of the absolute values of the Ampere hours into and out of this HVES instance.  

This pa";
CM_ SG_ 2633785075 HS_TotLifetimeEInp "The cumulative energy which has flowed into the High Voltage Energy Storage System over the lifetime of the battery system (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack). In multipack systems this parameter is the sum of the individual packs (See SPN 13367 (";
CM_ SG_ 2633785075 HS_TotLifetimeEOutp "The cumulative energy which has flowed out of the High Voltage Energy Storage System over the lifetime of the battery system (or Pack 1 in systems with only one pack). In multipack systems this parameter is the sum of the individual packs (See SPN 13368 ";
CM_ BO_ 2566841889 "Time/Date";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Seconds "The seconds component of the current time of day.  This should be reported as the seconds component of the current time at UTC (Universal Time Coordinate), a.k.a. GMT; however, it may be reported as the seconds component of the current time at a local ti";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Minutes "The minutes component of the current time of day.  This should be reported as the minutes component of the current time at UTC (Universal Time Coordinate), a.k.a. GMT; however, it may be reported as the minutes component of the current time at a local ti";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Hours "The hour component of the current time of day.  This should be reported as the hour component of the current time at UTC (Universal Time Coordinate), a.k.a. GMT; however, it may be reported as the hour component of the current time at a local time zone. ";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Month "The month component of the current calendar date.  This should be reported as the month component of the current date at UTC (Universal Time Coordinate), a.k.a. GMT; however, it may be reported as the month component of the current date at a local time z";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Day "The day component of the current calendar date.  This should be reported as the day component of the current date at UTC (Universal Time Coordinate), a.k.a. GMT; however, it may be reported as the day component of the current date at a local time zone.  ";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Year "The year component of the current calendar date.  This should be reported as the year component of the current date at UTC (Universal Time Coordinate), a.k.a. GMT; however, it may be reported as the year component of the current date at a local time zone";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Lcl_minuteoffset "The minute component of the offset between the UTC time and date and a local time zone time and date.  This is the number of minutes to add to UTC (Universal Time Coordinate) time and date to convert to the time and date in the local time zone .  The Loc";
CM_ SG_ 2566841889 Lcl_houroffset "The hour component of the offset between the UTC (Universal Time Coordinate) time and date and a local time zone time and date.  This is the number of hours to add to UTC, a.k.a. GMT, time and date to convert to the time and date in the local time zone. ";
CM_ BO_ 2566845729 "Ambient Conditions";
CM_ SG_ 2566845729 Barometric_P "Absolute air pressure of the atmosphere.";
CM_ SG_ 2566845729 Cab_InteriorT "Temperature of air inside the part of the vehicle that encloses the driver and vehicle operating controls.

Note: See also SPN 1691.  SPN 1662 is an additional diagnostic SP associated with cab temperature.";
CM_ SG_ 2566845729 Amb_AirT "Temperature of air surrounding vehicle.";
CM_ SG_ 2566845729 Eng_Intk1AirT "Temperature of air entering vehicle air induction system.";
CM_ SG_ 2566845729 Road_SurfT "Indicated temperature of road surface over which vehicle is operating.";
